headline: Nvidia Says Dell Is Shipping Blackwell AI Servers ‘At Scale’
summary: Dell Technologies is now shipping Nvidia’s Blackwell GB200 NVL72 AI servers in volume.  “Dell servers with NVIDIA GB200 are shipping at scale for a variety of customers, such as CoreWeave’s new NVIDIA GB200 NVL72 system,” Nvidia said in a blog post Tuesday.  The NVL72 is currently Nvidia’s top-of-the-line AI server and has 72 Blackwell GPUs linked together inside one server rack that measures roughly 2 feet wide, 4 feet deep, and 7 feet tall.
